dc_description_s: This data represents zoning for Waupaca County, Wisconsin in 2024, and includes the layers 'WAUPACA_GENERAL_2024', and 'WAUPACA_SHORLAND_2024'. [General: Rural zoning districts for townships that fall under Waupaca County Zoning. Zoning data is tax parcel based.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data for this county, please visit: [https://data2017-04-05t135915451z-waupacacounty.opendata.arcgis.com/][General: This file is rarely (if ever) fully representative of a dynamically changing landscape, the best that can be expected is data relative to a specific point in time.]
